Zac is oozing with birthday excitement! Show our sweet sentient slime buddy some love!

R - Needlework

Gwen can cast Needlework 3 times, but needs to hit an enemy within 8 seconds to unlock subsequent casts, dealing magic damage, slowing enemies, and applying Thousand Cuts. 

The first cast fires 1 needle, the second fires 3 and the final fires 5.

W - Hallowed Mist

Gwen spins up the Hallowed Mist to surround her for 5 seconds gaining armor and magic resist. Enemies outside the Mist cannot target her or hit her with any abilities. The mist will follow her the first time she tries to leave it, but will dissipate next time.
